        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This elegant black, gold-tipped *+1 striking fighting fan* is adorned with images of three golden leaves and a red rope tassel. If a creature is reduced to 0 Hit Points by a spirit fan, the golden leaves on the fan light up, providing illumination equal to that of a torch for 1 minute.",
