                    "frequency": "once per hour",
                    "effect": "You sweep the  *spirit fan* in the direction of a single target you can see within 30 feet, releasing the life energy in the form of a streak of golden light. The spirit fan goes dark. If the target is a living creature, the energy restores 3d8+8 Hit Points. If the target is undead, it takes 2d8+8 positive damage (DC 23 basic Fortitude save).",
